column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name],     &&& + cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type FROM #x x, #upload u, PhotoTag p WHERE u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID=p.objID  ORDER BY x.up_id
